(24, 84, 'Application', 'application', '<div class="t-content__body formatted">\r\n<p>The Avlite range of superior-quality aviation products are designed to withstand harsh environments, including prolonged U.V. exposure, and to operate unattended for years.</p>\r\n<br style="clear: both;" /> <a class="parent" href="#"><img class="post__img alignright" src="http://www.avlite.com/about/images/Amata-Air-Strip-Dec-06.jpg" alt="" width="255" /></a>\r\n<h3>Typical applications include;</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Barricade lighting (as per FAA Advisory Circular AC150/5370-2E)</li>\r\n<li>Taxiway Edge lighting</li>\r\n<li>Apron Edge lighting</li>\r\n<li>Obstruction Lighting as per ICAO LIOL Type A &amp; B</li>\r\n<li>Perimeter security lighting</li>\r\n<li>Temporary airstrip lights</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>The range of applications for Avlite products is limited only by the imagination of our customers, and their reliability and versatility have made them ideal for applications such as:</p>\r\n<a class="parent" href="#"><img class="post__img alignright" src="http://www.avlite.com/technical/images/Loxton-Air-Strip.jpg" alt="" width="275" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Roadway hazard markers</li>\r\n<li>Railway lights</li>\r\n<li>Docking lights</li>\r\n<li>Bridge lighting</li>\r\n<li>Perimeter lighting</li>\r\n<li>Mining haul roads</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br style="clear: both;" />\r\n<p>The Avlite award-winning design team prides itself on assisting our customers through purpose-built projects for applications that fall outside our standard product range. Please contact Avlite if you feel we can add value and enhance the safety of your current project.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>The Avlite Commitment:</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Avlite takes pride in manufacturing and supplying products that are of the very highest quality, each of which is the most advanced in its class.</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>Please Note: All Avlite products are intended as premium quality lighting products. The responsibility for the use of Avlite products rests entirely with the end-user, and Avlite is not committed by any undertakings or representations made by its distributors or dealers.</em></p>\r\n<div class="gallery gallery--2col">\r\n<div class="gallery_item"><a class="lightbox cboxElement" href="http://www.avlite.com/technical/images/montreal.jpg" rel="lightbox"> <img src="http://www.avlite.com/technical/images/montreal.jpg" /> </a></div>\r\n<div class="gallery_item"><a class="lightbox cboxElement" href="http://www.avlite.com/about/images/080808-SLR-009.jpg" rel="lightbox"> <img src="http://www.avlite.com/about/images/080808-SLR-009.jpg" /> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 27, '2013-12-26 01:43:38', 929, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-12-26 01:43:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 5, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(25, 88, 'Video Gallery', 'video-gallery', '<h2 class="section-title">AVLITE Video Gallery</h2>\r\n<div class="gallery-wrapper ">\r\n<div class="figure">\r\n<div class="figcaption" style="padding: 0 !important;">\r\n<h3>Avlite manufactures world-class solar aviation lighting systems</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="iframe-wrap"><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/8fMz_6VXwVE" frameborder="0"></iframe></div>\r\n<p style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; color: #0000ff;">Avlite Systems is a world-class solar aviation lighting systems manufacturer with a proven reputation for rapid, innovative, and agile technology solutions designed specifically for defense, government, civil and humanitarian aid operations in the most remote, toughest environments.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="figure">\r\n<div class="figcaption" style="padding: 0 !important;">\r\n<h3>Avlite Launches Heliport Lighting System</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="iframe-wrap"><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/MHeGQRytX6Q" frameborder="0"></iframe></div>\r\n<p style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; color: #0000ff;">Avlite solar heliport lighting system for emergency, temporary or permanent helipads and helidecks.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The system offers helicopter crews engaged in emergency medical services, search and rescue, law enforcement, humanitarian missions and defense a safer way to land and take off at night or in low-visibility conditions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 29, '2014-01-02 03:40:27', 929, '', '2014-01-02 03:59:23', 929, 929, '2014-01-02 03:59:23', '2014-01-02 03:40:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro